<SysML:Requirement id="60c20b91-1834-11ef-bd8c-a02942b134cf">
<externalId>
<val>3</val>
</externalId>
<name>
<val>Adaptability</val>
</name>
<owningPackage>
<ref refid="012edaba-70f5-11ec-aabc-f47b099bf663"/>
</owningPackage>
<package>
<ref refid="012edaba-70f5-11ec-aabc-f47b099bf663"/>
</package>
<presentation>
<reflist>
<ref refid="60c20b92-1834-11ef-8b4a-a02942b134cf"/>
</reflist>
</presentation>
<text>
<val>The Cyber-Physical-System shall be able to produce and represent a variety of bridge structures and adapt to their requirements
</val>
</text>
</SysML:Requirement>
<SysML:RequirementItem id="60c20b92-1834-11ef-8b4a-a02942b134cf">
<matrix>
<val>(1.0, 0.0, 0.0, 1.0, 676.0, 188.0)</val>
</matrix>
<top-left>
<val>(0.0, 0.0)</val>
</top-left>
<width>
<val>260.0</val>
</width>
<height>
<val>175.0</val>
</height>
<diagram>
<ref refid="01a97fa8-70f6-11ec-aabc-f47b099bf663"/>
</diagram>
<subject>
<ref refid="60c20b91-1834-11ef-bd8c-a02942b134cf"/>
</subject>
</SysML:RequirementItem>
<SysML:Requirement id="c24c2435-1834-11ef-a5e8-a02942b134cf">
<externalId>
<val>2</val>
</externalId>
<name>
<val>Production</val>
</name>
<owningPackage>
<ref refid="012edaba-70f5-11ec-aabc-f47b099bf663"/>
</owningPackage>
<package>
<ref refid="012edaba-70f5-11ec-aabc-f47b099bf663"/>
</package>
<presentation>
<reflist>
<ref refid="c24c72bf-1834-11ef-8483-a02942b134cf"/>
</reflist>
</presentation>
<text>
<val>The CPS shall be able to produce the necessary components of a bridge structure</val>
</text>
</SysML:Requirement>
<SysML:RequirementItem id="c24c72bf-1834-11ef-8483-a02942b134cf">
<matrix>
<val>(1.0, 0.0, 0.0, 1.0, 440.0, 189.0)</val>
</matrix>
<top-left>
<val>(0.0, 0.0)</val>
</top-left>
<width>
<val>210.0</val>
</width>
<height>
<val>158.0</val>
</height>
<diagram>
<ref refid="01a97fa8-70f6-11ec-aabc-f47b099bf663"/>
</diagram>
<subject>
<ref refid="c24c2435-1834-11ef-a5e8-a02942b134cf"/>
</subject>
</SysML:RequirementItem>
<SysML:Requirement id="2be43412-1836-11ef-8661-a02942b134cf">
<externalId>
<val>4</val>
</externalId>
<name>
<val>Monitoring</val>
</name>
<owningPackage>
<ref refid="012edaba-70f5-11ec-aabc-f47b099bf663"/>
</owningPackage>
<package>
<ref refid="012edaba-70f5-11ec-aabc-f47b099bf663"/>
</package>
<presentation>
<reflist>
<ref refid="2be482a2-1836-11ef-a983-a02942b134cf"/>
</reflist>
</presentation>
<text>
<val>The Physical part of the CPS shall be actively monitored during use.</val>
</text>
</SysML:Requirement>
<SysML:RequirementItem id="2be482a2-1836-11ef-a983-a02942b134cf">
<matrix>
<val>(1.0, 0.0, 0.0, 1.0, 975.0, 191.0)</val>
</matrix>
<top-left>
<val>(0.0, 0.0)</val>
</top-left>
<width>
<val>246.0</val>
</width>
<height>
<val>122.0</val>
</height>
<diagram>
<ref refid="01a97fa8-70f6-11ec-aabc-f47b099bf663"/>
</diagram>
<subject>
<ref refid="2be43412-1836-11ef-8661-a02942b134cf"/>
</subject>
</SysML:RequirementItem>
<SysML:Requirement id="50b72e14-1836-11ef-86ac-a02942b134cf">
<externalId>
<val>5</val>
</externalId>
<name>
<val>Production Feedback</val>
</name>
<owningPackage>
<ref refid="012edaba-70f5-11ec-aabc-f47b099bf663"/>
</owningPackage>
<package>
<ref refid="012edaba-70f5-11ec-aabc-f47b099bf663"/>
</package>
<presentation>
<reflist>
<ref refid="50b758e4-1836-11ef-a0b9-a02942b134cf"/>
</reflist>
</presentation>
<text>
<val>Based on the collected information through monitoring, the CPS shall be able to provide feedback to the digital representation of the structure</val>
</text>
</SysML:Requirement>
<SysML:RequirementItem id="50b758e4-1836-11ef-a0b9-a02942b134cf">
<matrix>
<val>(1.0, 0.0, 0.0, 1.0, 1258.0, 191.0)</val>
</matrix>
<top-left>
<val>(0.0, 0.0)</val>
</top-left>
<width>
<val>251.0</val>
</width>
<height>
<val>176.0</val>
</height>
<diagram>
<ref refid="01a97fa8-70f6-11ec-aabc-f47b099bf663"/>
</diagram>
<subject>
<ref refid="50b72e14-1836-11ef-86ac-a02942b134cf"/>
</subject>
</SysML:RequirementItem>
<SysML:Requirement id="4ddbe12b-1837-11ef-ab6b-a02942b134cf">
<externalId>
<val>1</val>
</externalId>
<name>
<val>Digital Representation</val>
</name>
<owningPackage>
<ref refid="012edaba-70f5-11ec-aabc-f47b099bf663"/>
</owningPackage>
<package>
<ref refid="012edaba-70f5-11ec-aabc-f47b099bf663"/>
</package>
<presentation>
<reflist>
<ref refid="4ddc088c-1837-11ef-942b-a02942b134cf"/>
</reflist>
</presentation>
<text>
<val>The CPS shall include a digital representation of the bridge structure, on which changes can be applied.</val>
</text>
</SysML:Requirement>
<SysML:RequirementItem id="4ddc088c-1837-11ef-942b-a02942b134cf">
<matrix>
<val>(1.0, 0.0, 0.0, 1.0, 155.0, 188.0)</val>
</matrix>
<top-left>
<val>(0.0, 0.0)</val>
</top-left>
<width>
<val>226.0</val>
